\c 11
\s UJesu ungena eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Kwathi besondela eJerusalema\x + Mat. 21.1-11. Luka 19.29-38.\x*, eBetfage leBethani\x + Mat. 21.17.\x*, entabeni yeMihlwathi, wathuma ababili kubafundi bakhe,
\v 2 wathi kubo: Hambani liye emzaneni okhangelene lani; lizahle lithi lingena kuwo lifice ithole likababhemi likhulekiwe\x + Mat. 21.2.\x*, okungazange kuhlale kulo umuntu; lilikhulule li\add li\add*lethe\x + Luka 23.53. Nani 19.2.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo uba umuntu esithi kini: Likwenzelani lokhu? Lithi: INkosi iyaliswela; njalo uzahle alithumele lapha.
\v 4 Bahamba-ke bafica ithole likhulekiwe lisesangweni ngaphandle, endleleni; basebelikhulula.
\v 5 Labanye kwababemi khona bathi kubo: Lenzani likhulula ithole?
\v 6 Basebesitsho kubo njengoba uJesu elayile; basebebayekela bahamba.
\v 7 Basebeliletha ithole kuJesu, baphosela izembatho zabo phezu kwalo, wasehlala phezu kwalo.
\v 8 Labanengi bendlala izembatho zabo endleleni; labanye bagamula izingatsha lamahlamvu ezihlahleni, bakwendlala endleleni\x + Joha. 12.12-15.\x*.
\v 9 Lalabo ababehamba phambili lababelandela bamemeza, besithi: \w Hosana\w**! Ubusisiwe ozayo ebizweni leNkosi;
\v 10 ubusisiwe umbuso kababa wethu uDavida, ozayo ebizweni leNkosi. Hosana kweliphezulu\x + Hlab. 118.26.\x*!
\p
\v 11 UJesu wasengena eJerusalema, lethempelini\x + Mat. 21.10,12,17.\x*; wathi esekhangele izinto zonke jikelele, sekuhlwile, waphuma waya eBethani labalitshumi lambili\x + Mat. 21.17.\x*.
\s Ukuthukwa komkhiwa
\p
\v 12 Lakusisa\x + Mat. 21.18,19.\x* bephuma eBethani, walamba\x + Mat. 21.17.\x*.
\v 13 Ebona umkhiwa ukhatshana, ulamahlamvu, wasondela ukuthi mhlawumbe angathola ulutho kuwo; njalo efika kuwo, katholanga lutho ngaphandle kwamahlamvu; ngoba kwakungesiso isikhathi somkhiwa\x + Luka 13.6.\x*.
\v 14 UJesu ekhuluma wathi kuwo: Kakungabi kusadla muntu isithelo kuwe kuze kube nininini. Labafundi bakhe ba\add ku\add*zwa\x + 11.20.\x*.
\s Ukuhlanjululwa kwethempeli
\p
\v 15 Basebefika eJerusalema; uJesu wasengena ethempelini waqala ukuxotsha labo ababethengisa lababethenga ethempelini; wasegenqula amatafula ababentshintshelana imali, lezihlalo zalabo ababethengisa amajuba\x + Mat. 21.12-17. Luka 19.45-47.\x*;
\v 16 wayengavumeli ukuthi umuntu athwale impahla adabule ethempelini\x + Luka 8.16.\x*.
\v 17 Wasefundisa, wathi kubo: Kakulotshiwe yini ukuthi: Indlu yami izabizwa ngokuthi yindlu yomkhuleko yezizwe zonke\x + Isa. 56.7.\x*? Kodwa lina seliyenze ubhalu lwabaphangi\x + Jer. 7.11.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ababhali labapristi abakhulu basebe\add ku\add*zwa, badinga ukuthi bangambulala njani\x + Mat. 21.45,46.Mark. 12.12. Luka 19.47.\x*; ngoba babemesaba, ngoba lonke ixuku lamangala kakhulu ngokufundisa kwakhe\x + Mat. 7.28.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Sekusihlwa, waphuma phandle komuzi.
\s Ukuzuza amandla ngokholo
\p
\v 20 Ekuseni kakhulu besedlula\x + Mat. 21.19-22.\x*, babona umkhiwa womile kusukela empandeni.
\v 21 UPetro wasekhumbula wathi kuye: \w Rabi\w**, khangela, umkhiwa owuqalekisileyo womile\x + 11.14.\x*.
\v 22 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Banini lokholo kuNkulunkulu.
\v 23 Ngoba ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Loba ngubani ozakuthi kulintaba: Phakanyiswa, uphoselwe olwandle; njalo engathandabuzi enhliziyweni yakhe, kodwa ekholwa ukuthi akutshoyo kuyenzeka, kuzakuba kuye loba yikuphi akutshoyo.
\v 24 Ngakho ngithi kini: Konke loba yikuphi elikucelayo likhuleka, kholwani ukuthi liyakwemukela, njalo lizakuba lakho\x + Luka 6.12. Seb. 3.16; 4.9. Gal. 2.16. Kol. 2.12. Jak. 2.1.\x*.
\v 25 Njalo nxa limi likhuleka\x + Mat. 6.5. Luka 18.11.\x*, thethelelani uba lilolutho olumelana lomuntu; ukuze uYihlo osemazulwini laye alithethelele iziphambeko zenu\x + Mat. 6.14.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa uba lina lingathetheleli, loYihlo osemazulwini kayikulithethelela iziphambeko zenu\x + Jak. 2.13.\x*.
\s Amandla kaJesu
\p
\v 27 Basebebuya bafika eJerusalema; kwathi ehambahamba ethempelini, abapristi abakhulu lababhali labadala beza kuye,
\v 28 bathi kuye: Izinto lezi uzenza ngaliphi igunya; njalo ngubani okunike leligunya lokuthi wenze lezizinto?
\v 29 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Lami ngizalibuza umbuzo\f + \fk umbuzo: \ft kumbe, \fq into\f* ube munye, njalo lingiphendule, khona ngizalitshela ukuthi ngenza lezizinto ngaliphi igunya.
\v 30 Ubhabhathizo lukaJohane lwavela ezulwini, kumbe ebantwini? Ngiphendulani.
\v 31 Basebekhulumisana, besithi: Uba sisithi: Ezulwini, uzakuthi: Pho kalikholwanga kuye ngani?
\v 32 Kodwa uba sisithi: Ebantwini; besaba abantu; ngoba bonke babemphatha uJohane, ngokuthi ungumprofethi ngeqiniso.
\v 33 Basebephendula bathi kuJesu: Kasazi. UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Lami kangilitsheli ukuthi ngenza lezizinto ngaliphi igunya\x + Mat. 21.23-27. Luka 20.1-8.\x*.
